Additional Notes:

-The technique used in styling of this web site is a mixture of modular and traditional approaches.

-You will find a mobile first implementation as default. Rules for larger screen sizes,
as well as mobile specific reusable/modular layout selector rules, are set or changed down below,
in the related screen media query. So, always be watchful about the prefixes to locate
the correct selector.

-Reused layout or modular selectors are tried to be implemented -so far as possible- independently
and have different prefixes regarding the screen size.

-When needed to refer the rule changes other parts of the document or other sections, the acronyms
below are used:

    MBSR: Mobile Specific Rules part of the css file
    MSSR: Medium Screen Specific Rules part of the css file
    LSSR: Large Screen Specific Rules part of the css file

    SF(file_name.liquid): Section File(section file name).
    TF(file_name.liquid): Template File(template file name).
    JSFU(function_name): Java Script Function(function name) Referred to scripts.js unless a specific
    section or template name is defined. Ex: JSFU(exampleFuncName) in SF(header.liquid).

